  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1523_5",
    "text": "(2）轴测法.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11937890703770922,
      0.5426820578594841,
      0.2282718289977818,
      0.5592133390337751
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1523",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1523_6",
    "text": "设计合适的投影角度，将现实空间的直角坐标系连同各轴 上的单位长平行投影到平面P上，使之成为投影平面P上的 一组“坐标系”，根据该“坐标系”各轴的方向、单位和投影的性 质，将空间图形在空间直角坐标系中的位置对应地画到平面P 上，得到一幅相应的平面图(图3—5).这种方法称为轴测法.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0790481952006453,
      0.5632036482827419,
      0.6235128050010083,
      0.6663816445774547
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1523",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1523_7",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
