    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1523",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1523_9",
    "text": "轴测法画出的平面图比较直观，常用来呈现产品、建筑物 等实物的外观效果.但是这类方法需要对投影角度以及在各方 向上的伸缩比例进行合理的设计，使平面图有较好的视觉效",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07985480943738657,
      0.8436653840672652,
      0.6235128050010083,
      0.9035200228017671
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1523",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1523_12",
    "text": "用轴洲法画的平面图 叫做轴测图。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
